"1 pound green beans","1 1/2 cups dried orzo pasta (8 oz.)","3  ears fresh corn (10 to 14 oz. each; see notes)","1/2 cup white wine vinegar","1/2 cup extra-virgin olive oil","1/2 cup minced shallots","2 tablespoons Dijon mustard","2 tablespoons minced fresh tarragon or 2 teaspoons dried tarragon","  Salt and pepper","2 cups cherry tomatoes (12 oz.), rinsed, stemmed, and cut in half"